Running the Amsterdam Density Functional package.

For bash:
. /home/apps/adf/adfrc.sh

For tcsh:
source /home/apps/adf/adfrc.csh

In your run scripts you may want to set the scratch directory to something
like (where project is a different name for different calculations):

setenv SCM_TMPDIR /state/partition1/${USER}/project
mkdir -p $SCM_TMPDIR
adf commands
rm -rf $SCM_TMPDIR

To run the graphical user interface:
adfjobs


